岀冷靜一下唔好聯絡住，請問我哋嘅關係之後會點，會唔會分手？"},{"pid":"939ff1be113805dcdcd837ef025044b2ca3df79b","tid":1957743,"uid":208629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4247a5774b0d8e3a53aab48b2b9711f5a66d26bc","tid":1957743,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b06e721b71b7496c56c6e515527749a1d0d1cd","tid":1957743,"uid":94037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329c0b987430a22cfb15082199e310c065127ff2","tid":1957743,"uid":311997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dc1aaad7a67132886efea92bf1c763392068c2","tid":1957743,"uid":344619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f407c896bccb379233d020f91ee453ef68cfda","tid":1957743,"uid":62819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"閒人一個想試下幫大家解決下煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即使係少少都好<br />\n塔羅牌對我嚟講就係rpg game入面嘅攻略咁樣，幫你睇下做咗行動A嘅話結果會係點，揀行動B嘅話結果又會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單嚟講就係用而家嘅情況推測最有可能發生嘅未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦想問嘅各位就麻煩睇清楚一下嘅指引啦<br />\n目標係想做到有問必答嘅（雖然唔知會唔會好慢）<br />\n都唔會限住一題開幾多張牌<br />\n但係唔跟指引嘅就對唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n1. 必須要有以下資料<br />\n問卜者稱呼<br />\n問卜者性別（愛情/友情適用）<br />\n對象稱呼（如有）<br />\n與對象現時關係（如有）<br />\n問題<br />\n<br />\n2. 問題要具體<br />\n錯誤示範:「我想問愛情/事業」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 時間性唔答 e.g.我幾時會出到pool/幾時搵到工<br />\n建議問題：我點樣做可以增加出pool機會/搵到工嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n4. 健康賭博生死唔答<br />\n<br />\n5. 每人一生限一條<br />\n你轉acc問其實我都可能唔會知嘅，講個信字啦我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nanyway 問題越具體你會得到越具體嘅答案同建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以係度留言又得tg我都得<br />\n怕羞/驚比人發現嘅就tg我啦<br />\ntg：<a href=\"https://t.me/mrkm4517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmrkm4517&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQys5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=d7978603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mrkm4517</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"問卜者稱呼 ：b<br />\n問卜者性別 : 女<br />\n對象稱呼 : a <br />\n與對象現時關係: 無再聯絡嘅所謂「朋友」<br />\n問題 ：<br />\n我好想同ex可以做番朋友，好似之前咁。所以想知我可以做啲咩挽救番大家嘅關係，唔變陌生人，大師可摸耳話我知將來同ex會係點，有冇咩建議可以比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大感謝"},{"pid":"61416322e246ed375c57559080ae1eb739c208a1","tid":1957743,"uid":62819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00db4c62f6d4ec88aebbfd9694b6b8892f85a62","tid":1957743,"uid":1968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"有嘅。你地其實各方面都幾夾，雖然兩個係好唔同嘅人，但係相處起嚟都唔錯，叫做可以互補。可以再認識下增進下感情呀。不過目前嚟講都係你會比佢更加在意呢段關係，所以關係發展嘅步調都會掌握係對方嘅手中。"},{"pid":"f0585520813f28a6d9c29d5e3f33169e85d8e2f9","tid":1957743,"uid":62819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97fdb3d9a79702e7762981c75c5cec31149ba881","tid":1957743,"uid":132359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問卜者稱呼 t<br />\n問卜者性別 女<br />\n對象稱呼 h<br />\n與對象現時關係 朋友<br />\n問題 有冇機會一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"暫時機會不大。佢而家望緊更加遠嘅地方，首要處理嘅唔係愛情，目前都係當你係朋友。不過樂觀啲諗佢對你係無反感嘅，所以都可以再相處多啲睇下有無機會呀。"},{"pid":"6cb3b7bea1dfd94692caf3